                {"src": "wesley", "attr": "Wesley's Notes", "html": "<p>By whom we have received — I and the other apostles. Grace and apostleship — the favour to be an apostle, and qualifications for it. For obedience to the faith in all nations — that all nations might be brought to the obedience of faith, to believe and obey. For his name — for the sake of Christ, and to his glory. The name is the person and the honor of the risen Son of God.</p>"},
